    <descriptionSet>
      <description>This card was sent from Enrico Caruso to Miss Izora O. Hunter. The card shows a self-caricature of Caruso, who was well known for his talent as a caricaturist. He published weekly illustrations in an Italian language newspaper for many years while he lived in New York. This card is one of the few in the collection sent by Enrico Caruso, as opposed to those sent to him.</description>
